<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

  <title>
    New smart action
  </title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />

  <script defer src="https://unpkg.com/peerjs@1.3.1/dist/peerjs.min.js"></script>
  <script defer src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container mw-540 p-3">
    <h3 class="mt-4">🤖 Telepresence Robot Portal</h3>
    <h5 class="py-2">Admin dashboard</h5>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid bg-dark">
    <div class="container mw-540 px-3 py-2">
      <div class=" d-flex align-items-center">
        <img src="/photos/<%= id %>.png" class="rounded-circle me-2" alt="" width="42" height="42" />
        <div class="d-flex py-2 me-auto">
          <h6 class="my-auto text-white">
            <b>
              <%= name %>
            </b><br />🏛️ <%= inst %>
          </h6>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex py-2">
          <form method="POST" action="/delete-smart-action/<%=actionUuid%>">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-light">❌ Cancel</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mw-540 py-3 px-4">
    <h6 class="mt-2">
      Print fiducial marker – 🎬
      <b class="text-primary">
        <%= actionName %>
      </b>
    </h6>

    <div class="progress mb-4">
      <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: 66%" aria-valuenow="66" aria-valuemin="0"
        aria-valuemax="100"></div>
    </div>

    <p>
      <b>1. </b> Download the generated fiducial marker and print with the
      same in-document sizing. The easiest way to do this is to print on A4
      paper. You can re-download this later, if needed.
    </p>

    <a type="button" class="btn btn-primary px-3 mb-3" href="ar/assets/marker/<%= actionUuid %>.pdf"
      download="<%= actionName %> Marker">✨ Download fiducial marker</a>

    <p>
      <b>2. </b> Attached the fiducial marker flat on a wall, at an
      appropriate height for the <i>Double 3</i>. If the wall is not white,
      leave a white border around the fiducial marker when you cut it out. You
      can attach as many as you like; they'll all work!
    </p>
    <form method="GET" action="/smart-actions">
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success px-4 mb-5">
        🏁 Finish
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>